VoiceControl instructions (updated)

See README.md and INSTALLATION.md for the current setup guide.

Summary:

Robot (Vision 60):
1) Install deps: espeak, alsa-utils
2) Run Flask+ROS2 backend (private backend)
3) Optional TTS test: espeak "Vision sixty speaking test"

Listener (Laptop/PC):
1) Install deps: ffmpeg, portaudio
2) pip install: openai-whisper torch pyaudio requests
3) Set FLASK_API in VoiceControl4.py
4) Run: python3 VoiceControl4.py

